welcome_message_body: Welcome to Cedar Park, where Southern charm meets modern convenience. Known for our beautiful parks, vibrant community, and family-friendly atmosphere, we invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Austin Executive Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers including restaurants, shops, and rental car services.

terminals.name: Private Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The private aviation terminal at Austin Executive Airport caters to private jet owners and offers luxurious amenities such as a VIP lounge and concierge services.

wifi.note: Complimentary wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Austin-Bergstrom International Airport houses all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Austin-Bergstrom International Airport is a smaller terminal used for low-cost carriers and regional flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
